OL,5,Csince Easter
OL,7,FTwo hospitals in Staffordshire have
OL,8,Fdeclared a 'critical incident' due to
OL,9,Fwhat they have called 'extreme
OL,10,Fpressure' since the Easter holiday
OL,11,Fperiod.
OL,13,FDeclaring this status means Royal
OL,14,FStoke University Hospital and County
OL,15,FHospital in Stafford can take
OL,16,Fadditional steps to try to maintain
OL,17,Fsafe services.
