OL,5,Csince Easter
OL,7,FAnn-Marie Riley, the Trust's Chief
OL,8,FNurse said: "We are currently
OL,9,Fexperiencing extremely high demand for
OL,10,Fall our services. Both Royal Stoke
OL,11,FUniversity Hospital and County
OL,12,FHospital in Stafford have been under
OL,13,Fextreme pressure since the Easter
OL,14,Fholiday period.
OL,16,F"We have therefore taken the decision
OL,17,Fto declare a critical incident. This
OL,18,Fhelps us to take additional measures
OL,19,Fto maintain safe services for our
OL,20,Fpatients.
