OL,7,F"We will always do our best for
OL,8,Fpatients and keep patients safe and
OL,9,Flocally we are working with our NHS
OL,10,Fand local authority partners to put in
OL,11,Fplace measures to ensure that people
OL,12,Fwho need hospital and emergency care
OL,13,Fcan get treatment quickly and to
OL,14,Fidentify and utilise any additional
OL,15,Fcapacity to allow us to discharge
OL,16,Fpatients that do not require hospital
OL,17,Fcare.
