OL,4,Chospitals due to 'extreme pressure'
OL,5,Csince Easter
OL,7,F"As anticipated, the pressure is
OL,8,Fgreatest in our emergency departments,
OL,9,Fwho are facing on-going challenges as
OL,10,Fpatients are unable to be admitted to
OL,11,Fbeds promptly.
OL,13,F"During this time the emergency
OL,14,Fdepartments will continue to see the
OL,15,Fsickest patients first, which means
OL,16,Ffor some patients there may be much
OL,17,Flonger delays for their treatment.
