OL,7,F"We continue to ask the public to help
OL,8,Fus by only using A&E in a serious or
OL,9,Flife threatening emergency and for
OL,10,Ftheir help when we're discharging
OL,11,Ftheir friends or loved ones to ensure
OL,12,Fthey're picked up from hospital as
OL,13,Fsoon as possible and have everything
OL,14,Fthey need at home.
OL,16,F"I would like to thank our staff for
OL,17,Ftheir on-going efforts during this
OL,18,Fextremely challenging period and the
OL,19,Fpublic for their understanding and co-
OL,20,Foperation."
